RACE.FOOTNOTES: HARRY'S ONTHEBEACH tracked in the three path, was roused approaching the quarter, angled out to the seven path into the stretch, and rallied past an inner pair in the final sixteenth. CAPTURETHELAUGHTER chased in the three path but was no factor from the five path in the stretch. PAPA KATZ always trailed around the five to seven paths.
